   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goodlife Pharma</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Goodlife Pharmacy Limited is a company established by Africa Chemist &amp; Beauty Care Inc. (ACBC) to be the leading branded pharmacy chain in East Africa. It presently consists of 5 recently acquired pharmacy stores operating under the brand name Mimosa in multiple locations in Kenya. Over the next 5 years Goodlife aims to rebrand these stores and acquire and establish new stores to create the leading branded pharmacy chain in East Africa (the Project).</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Project is expected to, among others; (i) increase availability of quality healthcare products to more than 2 million Kenyans per annum after the expansion is completed; (ii) create over 200 new direct employment for local communities during operations; (iii) provide professional development in customer service and business administration to Pharmacist and Pharmtechs employed by Goodlife via the Company&apos;&apos;s in-house training programs; (iv) act as a demonstration of the viability of pharmacy chains which will potentially result in consolidation in a presently fragmented pharmacy market. This in turn will result in lower costs and better quality for the consumers.</narrative>
  </description>
